7.25.20  2:50 pm   Was the "just got home, got no home" part in La de da planned from the start or did you just think "let's add this part and see how it goes" in the very last minute?

      That part is so absurd and yet it's so satisfying to listen. I don't know how you come up with this stuff.

      sometimes you have to think of it like the door. when you're building a room, and you're trying to build a way out of the room, ..... sometimes you need a door, and the trouble with that is that doors look nothing like the room, and they are very different from a room, mainly because you can't go inside a door. but this is the different mindset you have to be in sometimes, when you can't seem to get "out" of a song. usually i just think about doors and that does it for me
